                <h1>Southern University Location: Baton Rouge, LA</h1>
                <p>Southern University is located in Baton Rouge, Louisiana. Established in 1880, it is part of the Southern University System and serves as a historically Black university, providing a diverse range of educational programs and services to students. The campus is situated on scenic grounds along the scenic banks of the Mississippi River.</p>
